1__link\" href=\"https://katoristore.com/calendar\">\n            <span class=\"text\">月間カレンダー</span>\n          </a>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"header-nav-01__item\">\n          <a class=\"header-nav-01__link\" href=\"https://katoristore.com/flyer\">\n            <span class=\"text\">今週のチラシ情報</span>\n          </a>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"header-nav-01__item\">\n          <a class=\"header-nav-01__link\" href=\"https://katoristore.com/about\">\n            <span class=\"text\">大きな新鮮村について</span>\n          </a>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n      <div class=\"header-01__item pb50 mt50 show-sp\">\n        <ul class=\"list list--direction-row list--justify-center\">\n          <li class=\"list__item w-auto max100\">\n            <a class=\"button\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/katoristore_omura/\">\n              <img src=\"https://katoristore.com/wp-content/themes/bariyoka/images/header_img_02.png\" alt=\"かとりストア公式\">\n            </a>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"list__item w-auto max100 ml50\">\n            <a class=\"button\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/okinashinsenmura_omura/\">\n              <img src=\"https://katoristore.com/wp-content/themes/bariyoka/images/header_img_03.png\" alt=\"大きな新鮮村公式\">\n            </a>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </nav>\n</header>\n<div class=\"JsBgCover\"></div>\n\n<main class=\"main\">\n      <div class=\"head\n   head--bg-img-03 show-pc\">\n      <div class=\"head__inner\">\n        <div class=\"head__pd\">\n          <div class=\"head__item pt200 pb100 pt150-tab pb70-tab tar\">\n            <h1 class=\"text font-size-xxl font-size-27-sp font-size-23-sp-min font-color-special-01\">かとりストア企業情報</h1>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  \n      <div class=\"head\n   head--bg-img-08 show-sp\">\n      <div class=\"head__inner\">\n        <div class=\"head__pd\">\n          <div class=\"head__item pt200 pb100 pt150-tab pb70-tab tac\">\n            <h1 class=\"text tac font-size-xxl font-size-27-sp font-size-23-sp-min font-color-special-01\">かとりストア企業情報</h1>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  \n<section class=\"lead\">\n  <div class=\"lead__inner\">\n    <div class=\"lead__pd\">\n      <div class=\"lead__item tac\">\n        <h2 class=\"text font-size-xl font-normal\">\n          <span class=\"text--borderline\">&nbsp;経営理念&nbsp;</span>\n        </h2>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"lead__item tac mt20\">\n        <p class=\"text font-size-25 font-size-22-sp font-normal font-color-accent\">『お客様の立場で、まごころ込めて、良い品を』</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"lead__item tac mt15\">\n        <p class=\"text lh19 font-color-special-01\">\n          お客様の視点に立った営業活動をとり続け、<br>\n          「お客様に満足していただけること」が私たちの、最大の喜びです。\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"lead lead--bg-img-04 bg-position-top\">\n  <div class=\"lead__inner\">\n    <div class=\"lead__pd pt15\">\n      <div class=\"lead__box bg-color-white radius5\">\n        <div class=\"lead__item tac\">\n          <h2 class=\"text font-size-xl font-normal\">\n            <span class=\"text--borderline\">&nbsp;経営基本方針&nbsp;</span>\n          </h2>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"lead__item pl10 pl0-tab max750 w100p block-center mt30\">\n          <p class=\"text lh20 font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-color-accent\">一、私たちは、お客様・取引先・従業員を大切にし、感謝する会社を目指します。</p>\n          <p class=\"text lh20 font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-color-accent mt5\">一、私たちは、地域社会と調和し、その発展に貢献する会社を目指します。</p>\n          <p class=\"text lh20 font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-color-accent mt5\">一、私たちは、あらゆる法令を遵守し、社会倫理に適合する会社活動を実施します。</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"lead__item tac mt120 mt70-sp\">\n        <div class=\"position__item-05\">\n          <h3 class=\"text font-size-xl font-normal\">沿革</h3>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"lead__box bg-color-white border-02 border-color-accent radius5 mt-nega-30 max600-sp w100p-sp block-center-sp\">\n        <div class=\"lead__item max700 w100p block-center\">\n          <table class=\"table\">\n            <tr class=\"table__tr\">\n              <th class=\"table__th w20p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-bold\">・1969年</p>\n              </th>\n              <td class=\"table__td w80p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-normal\">前身の米穀店より「株式会社かとりストアー」を設立</p>\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-normal mt10\">「かとりストア原口店」オープン</p>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr class=\"table__tr\">\n              <th class=\"table__th w20p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-bold\">・1986年</p>\n              </th>\n              <td class=\"table__td w80p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-normal\">2号店「杭出津店」オープン</p>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr class=\"table__tr\">\n              <th class=\"table__th w20p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-bold\">・1995年</p>\n              </th>\n              <td class=\"table__td w80p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-normal\">それまでのテナント方式から、畜産部門・水産部門を直営化</p>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr class=\"table__tr\">\n              <th class=\"table__th w20p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-bold\">・2003年</p>\n              </th>\n              <td class=\"table__td w80p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-normal\">本店「原口店」の増床リニューアルに伴い、総菜部門を直営化</p>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr class=\"table__tr\">\n              <th class=\"table__th w20p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-bold\">・2004年</p>\n              </th>\n              <td class=\"table__td w80p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-normal\">2号店「杭出津店」閉店</p>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr class=\"table__tr\">\n              <th class=\"table__th w20p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-bold\">・2011年</p>\n              </th>\n              <td class=\"table__td w80p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-normal\">高齢者向けの無料お買い物バス運行開始</p>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr class=\"table__tr\">\n              <th class=\"table__th w20p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-bold\">・2012年</p>\n              </th>\n              <td class=\"table__td w80p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-normal\">大村市の商業施設「コレモおおむら」へ2号店「大きな新鮮村」出店</p>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr class=\"table__tr\">\n              <th class=\"table__th w20p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-bold\">・2017年</p>\n              </th>\n              <td class=\"table__td w80p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-normal\">コレモおおむらの電子マネー「コレEカード」利用開始</p>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr class=\"table__tr\">\n              <th class=\"table__th w20p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-bold\">・2019年</p>\n              </th>\n              <td class=\"table__td w80p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-normal\">「かとりストア原口店」 50周年</p>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr class=\"table__tr\">\n              <th class=\"table__th w20p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-bold\">・2022年</p>\n              </th>\n              <td class=\"table__td w80p w100p-sp pt15 pb15 pt10-sp pb10-sp\">\n                <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min font-normal\">コレモおおむら「大きな新鮮村」10周年</p>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </table>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"lead\">\n  <div class=\"lead__inner\">\n    <div class=\"lead__pd\">\n      <div class=\"lead__item tac\">\n        <h2 class=\"text font-size-xl font-normal\">\n          <span class=\"text--borderline\">&nbsp;会社概要&nbsp;</span>\n        </h2>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"lead__item max900 max600-sp w100p block-center mt60 mt50-sp\">\n        <table class=\"table\">\n          <tr class=\"table__tr\">\n            <th class=\"table__th w20p w100p-sp bg-color-accent-light border-bottom-01 border-color-accent pl20-sp\">\n              <p class=\"text tac font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min tal-sp\">社名</p>\n            </th>\n            <td class=\"table__td w80p w100p-sp pl45 pr45 pl35-tab pr35-tab pl20-sp pr20-sp border-bottom-01 border-color-special-02\">\n              <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min\">株式会社かとりストアー</p>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"table__tr\">\n            <th class=\"table__th w20p w100p-sp bg-color-accent-light border-bottom-01 border-color-accent pl20-sp\">\n              <p class=\"text tac font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min  tal-sp\">住所</p>\n            </th>\n            <td class=\"table__td w80p w100p-sp pl45 pr45 pl35-tab pr35-tab pl20-sp pr20-sp border-bottom-01 border-color-special-02\">\n              <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min\">〒856-0811　長崎県大村市原口町1050</p>\n              <div class=\"map mt30 mt20-sp\">\n                <iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3348.5832461250307!2d129.94511931493065!3d32.93560748092438!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x356aa71b190645fd%3A0x8f901def9842aa1!2z44GL44Go44KK44K544OI44KiIOWOn-WPo-W6lw!5e0!3m2!1sja!2sjp!4v1671079681236!5m2!1sja!2sjp\" width=\"100%\" height=\"275\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>\n              </div>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"table__tr\">\n            <th class=\"table__th w20p w100p-sp bg-color-accent-light border-bottom-01 border-color-accent pl20-sp\">\n              <p class=\"text tac font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min  tal-sp\">店舗名</p>\n            </th>\n            <td class=\"table__td w80p w100p-sp pl45 pr45 pl35-tab pr35-tab pl20-sp pr20-sp border-bottom-01 border-color-special-02\">\n              <p class=\"text font-size-18 font-size-17-sp font-size-16-sp-min\">\n                かとりストア原口店<br>\n                姉妹店 大きな新鮮村（コレモおおむら内）\n              </p>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"tabl